    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just what i tell myself to be kind... the truth is, they have their own lives, their own jobs and kids. seeing them rush over here just because i can't do basic things anymore feels wrong. it feels like i'm just dragging them down with me. wouldn't it be easier for everyone if they didn't have to worry about me anymore?",
